This paper discusses methods for feature selection and extraction in pattern analysis, which is a common topic in machine learning and computer vision. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), and cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
